{"tid":866190,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯社：侵爺啟動退出萬國郵政聯盟程序　不滿郵費政策偏向中國","createTime":"2018-10-17T16:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T03:33:57.000Z","uid":13663,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e06c9ee999244464ec6239383acd9196f1ba451","tid":866190,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:01:57.000Z","msg":"報道引述兩名官員消息人士稱，特朗普不滿現行國際間的郵務協議偏向中國及其他一些國家，變相造成美國企業的利益受損，又指從北京運送貨物去紐約的運費，比從三藩市運去美國東岸還要便宜，認為此對中國製造商有利，並指部分貨主藉此從中國運送類鴉片止痛劑芬太尼（Fentanyl）到美國。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士又表示，美國政府願意商談新的國際郵務政策，但如果不能達成新協議，將會退出聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n萬國郵政聯盟成立於1874年，1948年成為聯合國的專門機構，現在有192個成員國，聯盟協調各成員國之間的郵務政策，總部位於瑞士伯爾尼。<br />\n<br />\n牛三啦🐂<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/q0cairP4p5MFG/giphy.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fq0cairP4p5MFG%2Fgiphy.gif%20&h=2c08b78a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"431a264d8a6867b8e7cf16dd1dcb7a69e47cb2ee","tid":866190,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9f63ede74421c668171ad3b87a1ea3562588b57","tid":866190,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:04:09.000Z","msg":"加郵費＝加多次關稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e001af6089938890ef8992cfc917b332c9e7e34","tid":866190,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd232ab1e3fd2db21898ed29c7fcf4367d2ac8f","tid":866190,"uid":204245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:51:01.000Z","msg":"加息業主可以加租<br />\n加郵費貨主可以加價<br />\n同一LOGIC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1255b2c71653d32b1011eee7d7b38f0e8100822f","tid":866190,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cd232ab1e3fd2db21898ed29c7fcf4367d2ac8f","tid":866190,"uid":204245,"l